		<description><![CDATA[Some people love sports and have not lost an opportunity to be active. On the contrary, many people do not consider this possibility even though the doctor has recommended them exercise and there are many others who would start but never find the right time and use any excuse &#8211; to groundless fears &#8211; to [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://c713371.r71.cf2.rackcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/iStock_000017016138XSmall_-clu-2.jpg" alt="The excuses you away from the gym and how to combat them" align="left" style="padding-right:5px" width="200"/>Some people love sports and have not lost an opportunity to be active. On the contrary, many people do not consider this possibility even though the doctor has recommended them exercise and there are many others who would start but never find the right time and use any excuse &#8211; to groundless fears &#8211; to postpone the time. That may be your case. Here are some myths to be down, so nothing you away from the gym.</p>
<p>From small, Gonzalo always liked reading and getting lost in bookstores. Always kept his mind active but your body spent many hours sitting. He saw no problems with that and he even seemed to spend an hour a gym was a waste of time, it made no sense, he was not born to be a sportsman and was not able to make a single abdominal. Until he fell in love with a hyperactive woman who loved to dance and go biking outdoors whenever he had time and responsibilities allow.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s how Gonzalo bought a bike and set out to shoot, first once a week, then two and then whenever I had a moment. And so began taking salsa lessons to accompany the girl of his dreams!</p>
<p>That relationship did not last long, but enough to establish a link to Gonzalo for life with exercise. He realized that he could do more than sit-ups, it was not as boring as he thought, or that was not necessary to be a sportsman to keep moving. Moreover, the more exercised, slept better and felt more lucid reading and incorporate new knowledge.</p>
<p>As Gonzalo, many people have misconceptions or fears related to exercise. You can be one of them and you can also spend the same once you achieve incorporate these habits into your life.<span id="more-1367"></span></p>
<p>Marcela was quite active until she had her second child and got a lot of weight. Coupled with the time that he should devote to the baby and her eldest daughter, those extra kilos or pounds was enough to never resume an exercise routine. However, everyone knows that exercise can help you lose weight, which further appreciate your effort. Do not let shame you win!</p>
<p>Pamela, however, is afraid of everything. Want to look better but think that the treadmill can be hurt or in the bathrooms will give an infection. Someone told him to do some outdoor activity, which had no such risk, but not convinced, she&#8217;s already thinking that if it comes to riding a bike around the neighborhood may have a traffic accident and who knows how many other &#8220;dangers&#8221; but not allow you to start a healthy change in your life.</p>
<p>If any of these fears has come over you, remember that while these risks exist, are minimal. In any case, you can seek counseling with a coach to me explain how to use each machine in the gym and talk to your doctor if for any health reason there is any movement that you should avoid. Do not let this limit. Infections can also be prevented. AsesÃ³rate and cheer up!</p>
<p>Jose Luis, however, wants to resume his basketball weekends to keep busy after his divorce, but as he has abandoned many years ago, feels old and fears become the laughing stock of the group can not make those plays awesome he did in his youth.</p>
<p>There is nothing further from reality. If you do not exercise much, before starting to play the overnight is important to begin with gentle exercise and little by little, until you&#8217;re in shape. Moreover, if you are 40 years or older and you have not done a medical check and get an advantage before an intense workout. May initially not be as fast as your companions, but you may be surprised after a while, seeing the progress you achieve with your body.</p>
<p>In conclusion, unless you have a serious health problem, in which case it is important that you consult your doctor for advice, nothing is as an excuse to avoid an activity that will give you a better quality of life. Do not let your physical appearance stop you, nor shame, nor the lack of time, do not need to do one hour of daily exercise to feel the effects. Start with short routines of 15 to 30 minutes, anywhere: exercising at home, dedicating to gardening, replacing the car by walking to nearby places. Any excuse is good to keep your body moving, kicking butt!</p>
<p>Of course, it may hurt, but if you&#8217;re careful you will find it easy to avoid or detect them quickly. In this article we give you some guidelines to differentiate whether the pain is with exercise or whether it is an injury. And of course, if you have any particular health condition such as heart problems or joint, be sure to consult your doctor before starting any exercise routine.</p>
<p>Finally, try to have fun. Choose a physical activity that you like. There are many and varied! There are no excuses for not choosing a healthier lifestyle. And if you still can not decide, make sure you read this article in which we tell you how to establish an exercise routine without abandoning the attempt.</p>
